text: Eugenia pahangensis is a species of plant in the family Myrtaceae. It is a tree endemic to Peninsular Malaysia. Some populations are protected in Taman Negara.Kochummen, K. M. 1998. Eugenia pahangensis. 2012 IUCN Red List of Threatened Species.
